<plot>The film is set in a small town in the southern land of Abkhasia in the foothills of the Caucasian Mountains. Amra is the most beautiful girl in town. Her father, Mr Khasarman, is in charge of a cattle business. He is hosting Alou, who came here to practice veterinarian medicine and got hired by Khasarman. Amra and Alou fall in love at first sight. But the ancient traditions of the land are very conservative. Two local guys are now jealous and frustrated, because they are also in love with Amra. Amra's wise father Khasarman is helping his daughter to make the right decision.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?036294</url></doc>
